sequenceDiagram
    participant SP as Sidepanel
    participant SW as Service Worker
    participant CM as Cache Manager
    participant Gmail as Gmail Tab

    Note over SP,Gmail: Label Selection
    SP->>SW: selectionChanged {labelId, includeChildren, scope, scopeTimestamp, seq}
    SW->>CM: queryLabel(labelId, includeChildren, scopeTimestamp)
    CM-->>SW: {labelId, count, coLabelCounts}
    SW->>CM: getLabels()
    CM-->>SW: labels[]
    SW->>Gmail: tabs.update(url) — label/search hash
    SW->>SP: labelResult {labelId, count, coLabelCounts, seq}

    Note over SP,Gmail: Label Deselection
    SP->>SW: selectionChanged {labelId: null, ...}
    SW->>Gmail: tabs.update(url) — #all or scoped search
    SW->>SP: labelResult {labelId: null, count: 0, coLabelCounts: {}}

    Note over SP,Gmail: Cache Complete Re-query
    CM->>SW: cacheState {phase: "complete"}
    SW->>CM: queryLabel(lastLabelId, lastIncludeChildren, lastScope)
    CM-->>SW: updated {labelId, count, coLabelCounts}
    SW->>SP: labelResult (updated)
    SW->>CM: getLabelCounts(scopeTimestamp)
    CM-->>SW: counts
    SW->>SP: countsReady {counts}

    Note over SP,Gmail: Filters Off
    SP->>SW: filtersOff
    SW->>Gmail: tabs.update(url) — #inbox

    Note over SP,Gmail: User Navigation
    Gmail->>SW: tabs.onUpdated (hash change)
    SW->>SP: userNavigated (if not extension-initiated)
